name: Figma iOS UI Kit (Free)
description:
Figma iOS UI kit with iOS components, UI elements, and templates. Customize it to suit your project's needs!

This version features Figma iOS 13 UI kit templates made for iPhone X.

With easy-to-edit styles and customization options, you can make changes in bulk and save time. Perfect for smart designers, entrepreneurs, and agencies.

Featuring light and dark mode!

You can use these designs for your projects to help speed up your workflow. :-)
